      "B_en": "uses high dose per fraction, which sharply increases BED in low-α/β tissues. Serial organs such as spinal cord, brainstem, and optic apparatus can be severely damaged by a small-volume hotspot, so Dmax / D0.03cc is critical.",
      "C": "Dose constraints 需要考慮 dose per fraction、normal tissue α/β ratio、serial vs parallel organ、prior RT history、disease-site protocol，以及 conventional fractionation vs SRS / SBRT。",
      "C_en": "Dose constraints depend on dose per fraction, normal-tissue α/β ratio, serial versus parallel organ behavior, prior RT history, disease-site protocol, and whether treatment uses conventional fractionation or SRS/SBRT.",
      "ans": "C",
      "D": "有效放射生物劑量不只取決於 total dose，也取決於 dose per fraction、α/β ratio、treatment time ，以及正常組織是 serial organ 還是 parallel organ 。",
      "D_en": "The effective biological radiation dose depends not only on total dose, but also on dose per fraction, α/β ratio, total treatment time , and whether the normal tissue behaves as a serial organ or a parallel organ ."
