      "B": "包含 5-FU、leucovorin、oxaliplatin 與 docetaxel，通常術前每兩週一次共 4 次，術後再 4 次。",
      "B_en": "5-FU, leucovorin, oxaliplatin, and docetaxel, q2 weeks ×4 preop + ×4 postop.",
