      "C_en": "Glioma classification was historically based on histology. The 2016 WHO classification incorporated molecular features, and the 2021 WHO 5th edition further separated adult-type from pediatric-type gliomas and reorganized adult-type diffuse gliomas around IDH mutation status.",
      "ans": "C",
